  <li>What key factors should be considered when selecting a specific RAID level?</li>
  <li>How does RAID 0 compare to RAID 1 in terms of performance and redundancy?</li>
  <li>What are the main differences between RAID 5 and RAID 6?</li>
  <li>What role does parity play in RAID, and what are its advantages?</li>
  <li>In RAID 6, how many disks can fail without causing data loss?</li>
  <li>What is the minimum number of disks required to configure RAID 5 and RAID 6?</li>
  <li>Can you describe how RAID 10 works and its advantages?</li>
  <li>If cost is the primary concern, which RAID level would you recommend and why?</li>
  <li>Why is RAID 6 generally slower than RAID 5?</li>
</ol>

